this businessman,

61
00:03:32,921 --> 00:03:33,964
Jang Dae-hee.

62
00:03:34,548 --> 00:03:36,341
SEMINAR BY CHAIRMAN JANG DAE-HEE

63
00:03:47,477 --> 00:03:49,730
